          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "apr01s1t",
              "name": "s1title",
              "fill": "#333333",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Scene 1: スマートペンとギフトボックス",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "bold"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "apr01s1p",
              "name": "s1prompt",
              "fill": "#555555",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Prompt: A photorealistic lifestyle shot of a premium smart pen in an elegant gift box on a clean white desk, next to a handwritten congratulatory card and cherry blossom petals. Soft natural light from the left. Background shows a bright, modern office entrance beautifully blurred. Warm spring atmosphere, shallow depth of field.",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "apr01s1j",
              "name": "s1ja",
              "fill": "#555555",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Japanese: 高級スマートペンがエレガントなギフトボックスに入り、清潔な白いデスクの上に置かれている。手書きのお祝いカードと桜の花びらが添えられたフォトリアルなライフスタイル写真。左から柔らかな自然光。背景には明るいモダンなオフィスエントランスが美しくぼかされている。",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "apr01s1f",
              "name": "s1focus",
              "fill": "#0066CC",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Focus: 入社祝いにふさわしい高級感のあるスマートペン",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "bold"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "apr01s2",
          "name": "Scene 2",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "#FFFFFF",
          "cornerRadius": 8,
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 8,
          "padding": 16,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
